      "role": "user",
      "content": "Looks good. One more thing—since the new system is being touted as \"faster\" and more \"efficient,\" some of our older clients might worry that the personal touch and the deep, nuanced understanding of their specific tastes will be lost in favor of speed. Can you add a paragraph addressing that? Maybe something that subtly suggests that while the new engine is fast, there's a risk of it being a bit more \"robotic\" or less intuitive than the current personalized service they're used to? Just to manage their expectations.",
